00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:41.200
Adikku yang manis, kecil, dan imut!

00:13:41.880 --> 00:13:44.800
Jangan khawatir.
Kakakmu bersamamu.

00:13:47.400 --> 00:13:48.840
juara!

